Title: Last Resort
Plot: A man seeking the right diagnosis for his illness is willing to take on the hospital and the SWAT team to get it. He takes thirteen and several patients from the waiting room and puts them in Cuddy's office. To put an end to the crisis they must come up with the right diagnosis, treat the wounded, and hold off a SWAT team.
GuestStars: Zeljko Ivanek, Wood Harris, Tracy Vilar, Evan Peters, Sarah Thompson, Alex Sol, Natasha Gregson Wagner, Evan Jones, Marcus Chait, Jack Guzman
